        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="prose-dark mt-8">
        <p>
          The most important divergence is in the content opening. Decade-long SEO writing convention produced introductory paragraphs designed to set context, demonstrate depth, and reduce bounce rate. These introductions are friction for AI extraction. Eliminating them is the fastest single change you can make to improve citation frequency on existing content. For the full comparison, see <a href="/geo-vs-seo/">GEO vs SEO</a>.
